content: बृहस्पतिः [बृहतः वाचः पतिः पारस्करादि°] {@--1@} <ab>N.</ab> of the preceptor of the gods; (for the abduction of his wife Tārā by the moon, see under तारा to सोम.) {@--2@} The planet Jupiter; बुधबृहस्पतियोगदृश्यः <ls>R. 18. 76.</ls> {@--3@} <ab>N.</ab> of the author of a Smṛti; <ls>Y. 1. 4.</ls>
